arts.ttl: Bromley boss still ‘bit disappointed’ with maiden League Two campaign despite proving doubters wrong
arts.sum: Andy Woodman says that he feels disappointed not to see Bromley in the play-off spots despite what many consider to be a stellar first season in League Two. Bromley were among the favourites to face relegation at the start of the campaign after securing promotion to the EFL for the first time in their history as they beat Solihull Moors in last year’s National League play-off final.
